longBusinessSummary: Vision Values Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, provides network solutions and project services in Hong Kong, Mainland China, and Mongolia. The company is also involved in the property investment, logistics, and minerals exploration businesses; and provision of private jet and property management services. It offers telecom and enterprise solutions; and system maintenance services. Vision Values Holdings Limited was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Kowloon Bay, Hong Kong.
